text: Testosterone hexahydrobenzylcarbonate (brand name Lontanyl), or testosterone cyclohexylmethylcarbonate, is an androgen and anabolic steroid and a testosterone ester. ==References== Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Androstanes Category:Carbonate esters Category:Testosterone esters
title: Testosterone hexahydrobenzylcarbonate
